{"tid":2418078,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"衛報: 莊漢生透露自己是熱情的親華派 有意恢復與中國經濟對話","createTime":"2021-02-22T10:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T04:56:43.000Z","uid":75656,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"65e03a59e9c63fcdb9b5a6e586e0e63df94c6d72","tid":2418078,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:46:40.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒報道，首相約翰遜有意恢復與中國的經濟對話。<br />\n<br />\n《衛報》報道，約翰遜今個月12日在首相府與一批中國企業代表舉行圓桌會議，他透露自己是熱情的親華派，雖然中英兩國偶爾面對政治困難，但他決心改善兩國關係。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜說，期望透過重啟中英經濟財金對話與中英聯合貿易和經濟委員會，以恢復兩國之間的經貿討論。英國政府去年暫停與中方的大部分經濟對話，以抗議北京實施港區國安法。<br />\n<br />\n報道認為，約翰遜的講話表明他願意與中國簽署新的投資和市場准入協議，但可能觸怒保守黨內，要求對北京侵犯人權行為採取更強硬態度的成員。<br />\n<br />\n首相府不評論報道內容，但就說約翰遜對中國的看法是眾所周知，又說未有恢復兩國經濟對話的日期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576809-20210222.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576809-20210222.htm&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2Xjaf%2B7McJKZiP%2F5rhSwlYLA%3D&h=864ec599\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576809-20210222.htm&h=6a9d97cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576809-20210222.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7d28c964b779343131a074da766a78dff4df7116","tid":2418078,"uid":309558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:48:27.000Z","msg":"衛報可信?"},{"pid":"e8666a11f454ed7cad1eaaddb5eefb18d5d5c6e7","tid":2418078,"uid":75656,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:48:49.000Z","msg":"【六四30●檔案解密】英國為發大財 屠城翌年爭取放寬對中方制裁<br />\n<br />\n根據英國最新解密檔案，英方其實在六四事件發生後翌年已經開始立場軟化。在1990年4月底，負責香港事務的外交及聯邦事務部次長麥浩德（Francis Maude），要求制訂路線圖（critical path），爭取放寬歐洲理事會在六四事件後向中國施加的制裁。外交部遠東司司長戴維斯（Hugh Davies）向麥浩德提交完整的計劃時指出，英國有兩大原因需要放寬制裁，首先是「香港因素」，英國須透過改善對華關係，令兩國就香港事務拉回談判桌；其次便是英國企業需要「發大財」，中英關係緩和，可為英國企業改善營商氣氛，再加上英方須提供必要的優惠貸款，以幫助英企贏得重要商業項目（to release concessional finance necessary to win major business）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190604/IEIRZP3VL3WWC6AE55EG32UKIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190604%2FIEIRZP3VL3WWC6AE55EG32UKIQ%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2Xjaf%2B7McJKZiP%2F5rhSwlYLA%3D&h=bc44804e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190604%2FIEIRZP3VL3WWC6AE55EG32UKIQ%2F&h=85eff2f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190604/IEIRZP3VL3WWC6AE55EG32UKIQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuPePOa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuPePOa.png&h=eac8ef1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YQpKsAb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQpKsAb.png&h=e218f7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3MT5nk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3MT5nk.png&h=112163ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7PnHef4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7PnHef4.png&h=5b6a48e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nDGuPH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nDGuPH.png&h=a71f16e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjSDw3g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjSDw3g.png&h=31ca8408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0W42YJJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0W42YJJ.png&h=26c5ccc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UtX0Lo3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUtX0Lo3.png&h=efc5950f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">歷史重演？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"267577e83319d2f29c9fd4de8d9993d2beb2338a","tid":2418078,"uid":266503,"